little asswipe.

00:15:35.804 --> 00:15:38.472 position:7% line:89% align:start
I don't care if I'm a disgrace.

00:15:38.506 --> 00:15:41.208 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Kiyomasa yelling)

00:15:43.845 --> 00:15:46.346 position:27% line:83% align:start
And I don't care
if I'm pathetic.

00:15:48.883 --> 00:15:51.653 position:24% line:83% align:start
