00:17:26.714 --> 00:17:28.816 position:13% line:89% align:start
I finally stood my ground.

00:17:28.850 --> 00:17:32.419 position:24% line:83% align:start
And I finally took
down Kiyomasa.

00:17:33.721 --> 00:17:36.356 position:16% line:89% align:start
But unfortunately, Naoto,

00:17:40.260 --> 00:17:42.296 position:16% line:89% align:start
